.TH "SIMPLEWX" "1" "Mar 13, 2026" "" "SimpleWx"
.SH NAME
simplewx \- SimpleWx Documentation
.sp
SimpleWx is a Python wrapper around wxPython focused on rapid GUI development
with an API that mirrors the original SimpleGtk2/SimpleWx style.
.SH QUICKSTART
.SS Installation
.sp
Create a virtual environment and install dependencies:
.INDENT 0.0
.INDENT 3.5
.sp
.EX
python3 \-m venv venv
source venv/bin/activate
pip install \-U pip
pip install \-r requirements\-dev.txt
.EE
.UNINDENT
.UNINDENT
.SS Run an example
.INDENT 0.0
.INDENT 3.5
.sp
.EX
\&./venv/bin/python examples/samples/windows_basic.py
.EE
.UNINDENT
.UNINDENT
.SS Build documentation
.sp
HTML output:
.INDENT 0.0
.INDENT 3.5
.sp
.EX
make docs\-html
.EE
.UNINDENT
.UNINDENT
.sp
Manpage output:
